Program: The Forum
Title: Whistle-blowers and Rumour-mongers
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01j5xb0
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 14 Oct 2013
This week on The Forum, how can we distinguish between truth and rumour? And in what circumstances is telling the truth a really bad idea? Carrie Gracie talks to Secrets and Leaks author Rahul Sagar, about the ethics of leaking state information. Media expert Jayson Harsin explains the dark arts of the ‘rumour bomber’ and award-winning novelist Ana Maria Machado, with a Brazilian story of whistle-blowing gone wrong. Show less